title: Impact
desc:
- Can be played on top of <:red:1106234051129507932> or <:yellow:1106234135384699023> and vice versa.
- Whenever an <:impact:1106704414225485894> card is played, the next player gets an <:impact:1106704414225485894> Resistance stat, which is the number of <:red:1106234051129507932> and <:yellow:1106234135384699023> cards in their hand * 10%. They then draw cards equal to the number of the <:impact:1106704414225485894> card played or 5 if it doesn't have a number, reduced by their <:impact:1106704414225485894> Resistance.
